    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every aspect of the car has been meticulously preserved, from the flawless exterior paint to the pristine, odor-free interior. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine is exceptionally quiet and powerful, and the transmission shifts seamlessly. It has been garage-kept and strictly maintained according to the manufacturer's schedule, with full service records available. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle in showroom state.",
