    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is not currently in roadworthy shape. The exterior exhibits extensive rust across the frame and lower body panels, accompanied by multiple large dents and significant paint failure. Mechanically, the engine and transmission require major repairs or replacement, and the interior shows heavy wear with several tears in the upholstery. This car is best suited as a dedicated project for restoration or as a source for spare parts.",
